headline: Cintas (NasdaqGS:CTAS) Removed From Three Russell Value Indexes
summary: Cintas (NasdaqGS:CTAS) recently experienced significant index removals from the Russell 3000 Value Index, the Russell 1000 Value Index, and others, marking key shifts in market perception. Despite a 6% price increase over the last quarter, mirroring broader market trends, recent dividend affirmations and executive changes seemingly added stability amid these index exclusion pressures. The S&P 500 and Nasdaq reaching new highs likely provided additional support to Cintas's stock performance...
